    45Рєњ
    46Рєњ## Contributing
    48РєњmdBook is free and open source. You can find the source code on
    49Рєњ[GitHub](https://github.com/rust-lang/mdBook) and issues and feature requests can be posted on
    50Рєњthe [GitHub issue tracker](https://github.com/rust-lang/mdBook/issues). mdBook relies on the community to fix bugs and
    51Рєњadd features: if you'd like to contribute, please read
    52Рєњthe [CONTRIBUTING](https://github.com/rust-lang/mdBook/blob/master/CONTRIBUTING.md) guide and consider opening
    53Рєњa [pull request](https://github.com/rust-lang/mdBook/pulls).
    54Рєњ
