format/configuration/environment-variables.md
     1Рєњ# Environment variables
     3РєњAll configuration values can be overridden from the command line by setting the
     4Рєњcorresponding environment variable. Because many operating systems restrict
     5Рєњenvironment variables to be alphanumeric characters or `_`, the configuration
     6Рєњkey needs to be formatted slightly differently to the normal `foo.bar.baz` form.
