   286Рєњ#### `[output.html.search.chapter]`
   288РєњThe [`output.html.search.chapter`] table provides the ability to modify search settings per chapter or directory. Each key is the path to the chapter source file or directory, and the value is a table of settings to apply to that path. This will merge recursively, with more specific paths taking precedence.
   289Рєњ
   290Рєњ```toml
   291Рєњ[output.html.search.chapter]
   292Рєњ# Disables search indexing for all chapters in the `appendix` directory.
   293Рєњ"appendix" = { enable = false }
   294Рєњ# Enables search indexing for just this one appendix chapter.
   295Рєњ"appendix/glossary.md" = { enable = true }
   296Рєњ```
   297Рєњ
