format/markdown.md
     1Рєњ# Markdown
     3РєњmdBook's [parser](https://github.com/raphlinus/pulldown-cmark) adheres to the [CommonMark](https://commonmark.org/) specification with some extensions described below.
     4РєњYou can take a quick [tutorial](https://commonmark.org/help/tutorial/),
     5Рєњor [try out](https://spec.commonmark.org/dingus/) CommonMark in real time. A complete Markdown overview is out of scope for 
     6Рєњthis documentation, but below is a high level overview of some of the basics. For a more in-depth experience, check out the
     7Рєњ[Markdown Guide](https://www.markdownguide.org).
     8Рєњ
