guide/creating.md
     1Рєњ# Creating a book
     3РєњOnce you have the `mdbook` CLI tool installed, you can use it to create and render a book.
     4Рєњ
     5Рєњ## Initializing a book Рђд
    32Рєњ## Anatomy of a book Рђд
    36Рєњ### `book.toml`
    38РєњIn the root of your book, there is a `book.toml` file which contains settings for describing how to build your book.
    39РєњThis is written in the [TOML markup language](https://toml.io/).
      РєњРђд
    50Рєњ### `SUMMARY.md`
    52РєњThe next major part of a book is the summary file located at `src/SUMMARY.md`.
    53РєњThis file contains a list of all the chapters in the book.
      РєњРђд
    73Рєњ### Source files
    75РєњThe content of your book is all contained in the `src` directory.
    76РєњEach chapter is a separate Markdown file.
      РєњРђд
