guide/reading.md
     1Рєњ# Reading books
     3РєњThis chapter gives an introduction on how to interact with a book produced by mdBook.
     4РєњThis assumes you are reading an HTML book.
     5РєњThe options and formatting will be different for other output formats such as PDF.
     6Рєњ
     7РєњA book is organized into *chapters*.
     8РєњEach chapter is a separate page.
     9РєњChapters can be nested into a hierarchy of sub-chapters.
    10РєњTypically, each chapter will be organized into a series of *headings* to subdivide a chapter.
